      <description>&lt;p&gt;Yet another great day outdoors! We plan on doing more technical and/or longer hikes with Shasta and today was one of those &amp;lsquo;dry-runs&amp;rsquo;. We were out there in the woods for about 3.5 hours and she did terrific!&lt;/p&gt;
